A bed protecting mat is an essential part of a baby care kit. It protects the mattress from getting soiled. Quick Dry Sublimation Print Gold Butterfly makes a good addition to your baby care kit. This fade-resistant bed protector has an absorption capacity that is 8 times its weight. The multiple layers provide\xa0utmost protection and deters any chances of your little one’s bed getting soiled. There is absolutely no chance of bacterial and fungal infection or allergies owing to the anti-allergic and dust mite-resistant nature of Quick Dry’s bed protector. Measuring 70 cm in length and 50 cm in width this bed protector from the house of Quick Dry baby care products is washable upto 90 degree C and dries up no time. This bed protecting mat is autoclavable upto 25 times. Quick Dry Sublimation Print ultra-light bed protector can be used suitably for both boys and girls.
